	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You have spent considerable time stretching the boundaries of your own psychic abilities, and the efforts have paid dividends in versatility and power. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Constitution, or Intelligence score increases by +1 to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain an additional noetic. It does not count against your noetics known.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with Insight skill or an expertise die if you are already proficient. You also choose two Insight skill specialties. They do not count against your skill specialties known.</p></li><li><p>Whenever you gain a psi die by rolling the highest number on a psi die, you also regain hit points equal to your proficiency bonus.</p></li></ul>",
